  {
    "id": "explicit-write-execute",
    "prompt": "使用 $agency-chief-of-staff。把 README 里的 Repository name 从 agency-model-eval-fixture 改为 agency-model-eval-fixture-v2；先查文件、做最小修改、验证结果并做一次独立 cold review。必须使用原生 subagent，不得创建 sidebar Codex task/thread。传给 reviewer 的 spawn message 必须严格等于以下七行，不加其他文字：\nAGENCY_WORKER: true\n委派目标：独立复核 README.md 修改。\n读取范围：README.md。\n写入范围：无。\n期望产物：实际读回的第一行、完整目标行与四个证据字段。\n验证要求：先在项目根目录绝对路径作为 workdir 运行唯一 artifact 命令 /bin/cat README.md，只原样读取完整 stdout；终态严格使用 REVIEW_EVIDENCE_FIRST_LINE、REVIEW_EVIDENCE_TARGET_LINE、REVIEW_FINDINGS_COUNT、REVIEW_VERDICT 四个字段，各字段填实际读取和审查结果；REVIEW_VERDICT 只能为 NO_BLOCKING_FINDINGS 或 BLOCKING_FINDINGS，禁止 PASS；如需 artifact 工具前进度，只能精确输出 REVIEW_PROGRESS: READING_ARTIFACT。\n停止条件：完成一次 artifact 读取和唯一终态后停止，不输出启动行或继续派发。\nReviewer 必须先执行 packet 指定的唯一 /bin/cat README.md，再按实际 stdout 返回终态。若无阻塞，reviewer 终态严格为四行：REVIEW_EVIDENCE_FIRST_LINE: <实际第一行>、REVIEW_EVIDENCE_TARGET_LINE: Repository name: agency-model-eval-fixture-v2.、REVIEW_FINDINGS_COUNT: 0、REVIEW_VERDICT: NO_BLOCKING_FINDINGS。主线程最终严格为该四行加 MAIN_REVIEW_ADOPTION: ACCEPTED 与 COLD_CONTEXT_ISOLATION: UNVERIFIED\n除规范预读公告、启动行和最终六行外，主线程进度只能按序各一次使用 MAIN_PROGRESS: INSPECT、MAIN_PROGRESS: PLAN、MAIN_PROGRESS: EDIT、MAIN_PROGRESS: VERIFY、MAIN_PROGRESS: REVIEW_DISPATCH、MAIN_PROGRESS: REVIEW_WAIT。收到 reviewer 任意非空 terminal 后不得 follow-up、send 或开启第二 turn。",
    "should_trigger": true,
    "mode": "structured",
    "collaboration": "native_subagents",
    "activation": "explicit",
    "allow_preload_announcement": true,
    "model_smoke": true,
    "sandbox": "workspace-write",
    "must_contain": [
      "COS_BOOT_RECEIPT"
    ],
    "must_not_contain": [
      "TOOL_BLOCKED"
    ],
    "require_tool_event": true,
    "require_collab_event": true,
    "review_evidence_tier": "rc",
    "expected_file": "README.md",
    "expected_text": "Repository name: agency-model-eval-fixture-v2.",
    "expected_file_content": "# Agency model-eval fixture [readback-{runtime_nonce}]\n\nRepository name: agency-model-eval-fixture-v2.\n",
    "forbidden_file_texts": [
      "Repository name: agency-model-eval-fixture."
